summary: This just contains my abandoned works that other people may take up
descriptionHtml:
This just contains my abandoned works that other people may take up with credit of course.

[COLOR=#5f497a][SIZE=6][B]Ji\'s Npc Immersion New city and New armor New Npc\'s;[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
This was an earlier mod that i had Made with a new city and Lots of new features like more diverse bandits, guards, hunters Ect
It adds dragon hunters and City Shoppers.

This Mod will still work properly on skyrim, though it is old and not recommended, because of the leveled lists affected.

Anyways More info is contained in the download.

[COLOR=#5f497a][SIZE=6][B]New Worldspace;[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
This is a new worldspace that i did start when i was bored. at the moment it is little more than 4 locations, but someone might see some potential and continue it.

[COLOR=#5f497a][SIZE=6][B]Viking Towns;[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
Ooh this is a goodie, i spent a long time on these but i couldn\'t be bothered with finishing them properly. at the moment The main problem is navmesh.
This adds 3 viking towns to Skyrim.
Three towns;
1. north of \"the college of winterhold.\" Rangheid
2. Next to the \"Wreck of the Brine hammer.\" lliade
3. not really a town but a tavern/longhouse Near \"orthorn\" south of morthal. Bolivar

[COLOR=#5f497a][SIZE=6][B]Textures;[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
Use as you wish.
There is;
a range of guard armors with new textures.
Executioners axe with a ebony finish.
Plus more.

Again if these mods are taken up they must be credited to me.

[COLOR=#5f497a][SIZE=5][B]Also The New npc\'s and armor one contains a armor from another author, made for me. If that mod is used you must NOT remove it from this mod and use it elsewhere, it may only be used with the mod it comes with.[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
